query:
SELECT DISTINCT ON (o.uri)
                o.origin_uid,
                o.uri,
                qfr.name AS failure_reason,
                qf.queried_at
            FROM origin o
            JOIN query_failure qf ON o.id = qf.origin_id
            JOIN query_failure_reason qfr ON qfr.id = qf.failure_reason_id
            ORDER BY o.uri, qf.queried_at DESC
